snippet.title: Freerice:  Have Fun, Get Smarter, Help End Hunger
snippet.description:
Every question you answer correctly raises 10 grains of rice for the World Food Programme (WFP) to support its work saving and changing lives around the world.

Get the app on iOS and Android today: freerice.com/apps
Or visit freerice.com to play in your browser!
